## Layout

```
- No app header in this section
- Root container: display flex, flex-direction column, height 100vh
- Max-width: 390px, horizontally centered in viewport
- Safe area: padding-top env(safe-area-inset-top), 
             padding-bottom env(safe-area-inset-bottom)
- Zone distribution (proportional flex values):

  topGap:              flex 0.07
  chatbox:             flex 0.33
  gapChatboxToLabel:   flex 0.03
  exploreLabel:        flex 0.02
  gapLabelToCircle:    flex 0.06
  practiceCircle:      flex 0.33
  bottomGap:           flex 0.03
```

All flex values are proportional — implement as `flex: N` within a 
column flex container. No hardcoded pixel heights on zones.

Typography: use DESIGN.md definitions throughout.

