## Implementation Notes (Web-specific)

```
- All flex zone transitions: CSS transition on flex property, 
  duration 250ms, ease-out
- Drag interactions: implement via pointer events (pointerdown, 
  pointermove, pointerup) for cross-device compatibility
- Press and hold: use pointerdown + setTimeout(2300ms) combination
- Blur effect: CSS filter: blur(8px) on surrounding elements
- Countdown ring: SVG circle with stroke-dashoffset animation
- Recording (Speak): Web Audio API / MediaRecorder API
- Conversation state persistence: localStorage (session only)
- No React Native APIs — pure React + CSS
```

